---
title: Speedy Steak Fajitas with Bell Peppers and Hot Sauce Crema
description: These steak fajitas will put some pep in your step—and not just because they’re loaded with bell *pep*-pers. They’re also super-fast and simple to make, helping you hustle and bustle toward dinnertime. Warm flour tortillas are stuffed full and topped with spicy sour cream and a sprinkle of cheddar cheese. And while the prep may be fast, we’re pretty sure you’ll want to stop to appreciate the fiesta of flavors that each fajita holds.
